India Says Inflation Will Be Under Pressure Until December

-- B y   T u s h a r   D h a r a
-- 
2011-10-18T09:49:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-18/india-says-inflation-will-be-under-pressure-until-december.html
India expects headline inflation
rate to be “under pressure” until December and the nation’s
economic growth may be lower than estimated in the year ending
March, the  finance ministry  said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
